lu.uni.geko.util.bridges
Class JavaBridge

java.lang.Object
  lu.uni.geko.util.bridges.JavaBridge

public final class JavaBridge
extends Object

A utility class hiding details of the Java platform API for recurring tasks that are not project-specific.

(Note that it is disputable whether this class conforms to the bridge pattern as we are currently only providing one implementation and the "abstractions" can be regarded as low-level.)
